{"tid":1815651,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下自己減肥減到咁係咪正常？","createTime":"2020-01-07T16:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T02:52:03.000Z","uid":235588,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"913537a08ad920f77c4eaa90cfc65c0c484cac80","tid":1815651,"uid":235588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T16:18:44.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟高17X，依加63kg。早幾年（大約16、17歲）曾經瘋狂節食，令體重係短短幾個月減咗十幾公斤，減到得返唔夠六十公斤。最大問題係胸對上個啲骨突到出嚟，有啲皮包骨咁。但肚位置就如常。<br />\n<br />\n另外，手臂好幼，同女人個啲差唔多咁。但下半身又好肥，可能長期坐得耐，大腿好粗。依加我連一下掌上壓都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依加廿歲出頭想練大隻，但發覺好似搞壞咗身體，依加返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想問下我應該點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c95fecd64a133dbd86a303cdb5ffa39663d6c04","tid":1815651,"uid":58392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T16:19:41.000Z","msg":"有圖會易啲討論"},{"pid":"8db124c7faa749715be1af8e994c0105ba52736e","tid":1815651,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T16:25:16.000Z","msg":"圖呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049caed57b8629fdebd9f480be649cc012210dd9","tid":1815651,"uid":235588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3c95fecd64a133dbd86a303cdb5ffa39663d6c04","tid":1815651,"uid":58392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T16:19:41.000Z","msg":"有圖會易啲討論"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T16:25:31.000Z","msg":"青 唔好意思 驚自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im